The integrity of the MS. selected as the groundwork of the present edition having thus been, in all essentia] respects, preserved, the following modifications have been deemed advisable. The original consists of two distinct portions, and alphabetical arrangements, a nominate, and a verbale, according to the usage, of which other instances occur in contemporary works of a similar nature.
